	0.125
	~	Dmnl
	~	Other studies found that a substantial part of the carbon from permafrost \
		will be released as CO2 (the ratio depending on moisture). The ratio is \
		highly uncertain: http://www.pik-potsdam.de/ \
		anders/publications/schneider_meinshausen11.pdf
	|

Time_to_melt_greenland_ice_at_the_reference_delta_temp=
	4000
	~	yr
