		pg 343
	|

Fraction_of_earth_surface_as_ocean=
	0.7
	~	fraction
	~		|

Time_to_reach_C_equilibrium_between_atmosphere_and_ocean=
	90
	~	yr [0,150,10]
	~	system-wide calibration against Global Carbon Project data, esp 1959 to \
		2020 https://essd.copernicus.org/articles/12/3269/2020/ see also ARCHER, \
		D. (2009). The Long Thaw: How Humans Are Changing the Next 100,000 Years \
		of Earth’s Climate (REV-Revised). Princeton University Press. \
		https://doi.org/10.2307/j.ctvct0042 who argues for a long time, longer \
		than 100 years.
	|

