fa_to_gl[region]=
	MIN ( Max_forest_cut_after_policy[region], MIN ( Forest_land[region],  MAX ( 0 , Grazing_land_gap\
		[region]) ) * Fraction_of_grazing_land_gap_closed_by_cutting_forests[region])
	~	Mha/y
	~	First (MIN) you cannot use more land for grazing land than you have forest land, and \
		second (MAX) you only want to develop grazing land if need > actual i.e. \
		gap > 0
		Finally, all is embedded in another MIN function in case there is a policy \
		in place to stop forest cutting.
	|

