	0.055, 0.3, 0.3, 0.0939, 0.2541, 0.0939, 0.069, 0.075, 0.055, 0.1
	~	Dmnl
	~	GET XLS CONSTANTS('e4a-exo.xlsx', 'para' , 'c39' )
