Cohort_0_to_4[region]= INTEG (
	Births[region]-Aging_4_to_5[region]-dying_0_to_4[region],
		Cohort_0_to_4_in_1980[region])
	~	Mp
	~	Hist from https://population.un.org/wpp/Download/Standard/Population/ File POP/7-1: \
		Total population (both sexes combined) by five-year age group, region, \
		subregion and country, 1950-2100 (thousands)
		GET XLS DATA('e4a-exo.xlsx', 'ts' ,'1', 'D222' )
	|

