	.
********************************************************~
		Taking the Stella model back to Vensim because the Stella Game Interface \
		is too restrictive. Thus I need to move to open source, but the Stella \
		equation viewer does not list equations in the order of execution when \
		region=region.element
	|

region:
	us, af, cn, me , sa, la, pa, ec, eu, se
